## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="bdf3f-178">此屬性會擷取僅取代字串的項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bdf3f-178">This property retrieves only the replacement strings for the entry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bdf3f-179">若要擷取完整的訊息，請參閱<xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogEntry.Message%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bdf3f-179">To retrieve the full message, read the <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogEntry.Message%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="bdf3f-180"><xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogEntry.ReplacementStrings%2A>屬性包含的事件記錄檔項目中所使用的取代字串的當地語系化的版本。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bdf3f-180">The <xref:System.Diagnostics.EventLogEntry.ReplacementStrings%2A> property contains the localized versions of replacement strings that are used in the event log entry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bdf3f-181">如果您提供資源檔包含每個應用程式的目標語言的字串，您可以發出該電腦使用的語言中的事件記錄檔訊息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bdf3f-181">If you provide resource files that contain strings in each target language for your application, you can emit event log messages in the language that is used on that computer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bdf3f-182">若要這樣做，請建立的執行個體<xref:System.Resources.ResourceManager>包含取代字串的資源組件的類別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bdf3f-182">To do that, create an instance of the <xref:System.Resources.ResourceManager> class for the resource assembly that contains your replacement strings.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bdf3f-183">第一個參數<xref:System.Resources.ResourceManager.%23ctor%28System.String%2CSystem.Reflection.Assembly%29>建構函式會識別要使用的資源組件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bdf3f-183">The first parameter of the <xref:System.Resources.ResourceManager.%23ctor%28System.String%2CSystem.Reflection.Assembly%29> constructor identifies the resource assembly to be used.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bdf3f-184">使用<xref:System.Resources.ResourceManager.GetString%2A>該執行個體，提供當地語系化的訊息記錄事件的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bdf3f-184">Use the <xref:System.Resources.ResourceManager.GetString%2A> method of that instance to supply localized messages for log events.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="bdf3f-185">下列程式碼自動會將訊息設定為目前的文化特性的語言。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bdf3f-185">The following code automatically sets the message to the language for the current culture.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
ResourceManager LocRM = new ResourceManager("ReplacementStrings.TestStrings",   
      typeof(Program).Assembly);  
EventLog e1 = new EventLog("LocTest", "MyMachine", "LocTest");  
// Get the string associated with the current culture.  
e1.WriteEntry(LocRM.GetString("strMessage"),  
   EventLogEntryType.Information);  
```
